  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large clay pot or Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, cinnamon, and turmeric and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the fish fillets and cook until browned on both sides, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped apricots, prunes, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Pour in 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 10-15 minutes or until the fish is cooked through.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley or cilantro, if desired."
